I'll help you get warmed up! Let me explore your current directory to see what we're working with.

<Bash>
pwd
ls -la
</Bash>

Great! I can see you're in `D:\AI\cc_pro`. This appears to be a clean workspace. Let me also check what directories and files are available:

<Bash>
find . -type f -name "*.py" -o -name "*.js" -o -name "*.ts" -o -name "*.json" -o -name "*.md" -o -name "*.txt" | head -20
</Bash>

Perfect! I'm ready to help you with any file searching, code analysis, or development tasks you have in mind. What would you like to work on today?
